pk.sim.1 <- function(n=10000,p1=0.6,p2=0.8,p3=0.5,draw=FALSE){
  ## 
  
  # 
  pk.end <- function(s){
    # 3-0
    if(s[[1]]==3 & abs(s[[3]]-s[[2]])==3) return(TRUE)
    # 1
    if(s[[1]]==4 & abs(s[[3]]-s[[2]])>1) return(TRUE)
    # 
    if(s[[1]]>4 & s[[3]]!=s[[2]]) return(TRUE)
    
    # 
    return(FALSE)
  }
  
  # 
  pk.trans <- function(s, team=c("A","B")){
    p <- runif(1)
    
    # A
    if(team=="A"){
      # 
      if(s[[2]]==s[[3]]){
        if(p<p1) s[[2]] = s[[2]]+1  #  
      }
      # 
      else if(s[[2]]>s[[3]]){
        if(p<p2) s[[2]] = s[[2]]+1  # 
      }
      # 
      else{
        if(p<p3) s[[2]] = s[[2]]+1  # 
      }
    }
    # B
    else{
      # 
      if(s[[2]]==s[[3]]){
        if(p<p1) s[[3]] = s[[3]]+1  #  
      }
      # 
      else if(s[[3]]>s[[2]]){
        if(p<p2) s[[3]] = s[[3]]+1  # 
      }
      # 
      else{
        if(p<p3) s[[3]] = s[[3]]+1  # 
      }
    }
    return(s)
  }
  
  # 
  pk.ABAB <- function(){
    s <- c(0,0,0)  # 
    while (!pk.end(s)) {
      s[[1]] <- s[[1]]+1
      
      # A
      s <- pk.trans(s,team = "A")
  
      # B
      s <- pk.trans(s,team = "B")
    }
    return(s[[2]]>s[[3]])
  }
  pk.ABBA <- function(){
    s <- c(0,0,0)  # 
    while (!pk.end(s)) {
      s[[1]] <- s[[1]]+1
      
      # AB
      if(s[[1]]%%2){
        # A
        s <- pk.trans(s,team = "A")
  
        # B
        s <- pk.trans(s,team = "B")
      }
      # BA
      else{
        # B
        s <- pk.trans(s,team = "B")
  
        # A
        s <- pk.trans(s,team = "A")
      }
    }
    return(s[[2]]>s[[3]])
  }

  ## 
  r1 <- vector("logical",n)
  r2 <- vector("logical",n)
  for (i in 1:n) {
    r1[[i]] <- pk.ABAB()
    r2[[i]] <- pk.ABBA()
  }
  
  ## 
  if(draw){
    library(tidyverse)
    y1 <- accumulate(r1,`+`)/(1:n)
    y2 <- accumulate(r2,`+`)/(1:n)
    draw <- tibble(x=1:n,y1=y1,y2=y2) %>% 
      ggplot(aes(x=x))+
      geom_line(aes(y=y1,color=paste("ABAB,mean=",y1[[n]])))+
      geom_line(aes(y=y2,color=paste("ABBA,mean=",y2[[n]])))+
      labs(color="color",x="Simulation times",y="Ergodic mean",
           caption = paste("p1=",p1,",p2=",p2,",p3=",p3,sep = ""))
  }
  
  return(list(m1=mean(r1),m2=mean(r2),draw=draw))
}

pk.sim.3 <- function(n=10000,p.A=0.7,q.B=0.68,delta=0.05,alpha=0.05){
  ## 
  
  # 
  pk.end <- function(s){
    # 3-0
    if(s[[1]]==3 & abs(s[[3]]-s[[2]])==3) return(TRUE)
    # 1
    if(s[[1]]==4 & abs(s[[3]]-s[[2]])>1) return(TRUE)
    # 
    if(s[[1]]>4 & s[[3]]!=s[[2]]) return(TRUE)
    
    # 
    return(FALSE)
  }
  
  # 
  pk.AtoB <- function(s){
    p <- runif(2)
    n <- s[[2]]-s[[3]]
    if(p[[1]]<p.A+delta+n*alpha){
      s[[2]]<- s[[2]]+1
      if(p[[2]]<q.B-(n+1)*alpha) s[[3]] <- s[[3]]+1
    }else{
      if(p[[2]]<q.B+delta-n*alpha) s[[3]] <- s[[3]]+1
    }
    s[[1]] <- s[[1]]+1
    s
  }
  pk.BtoA <- function(s){
    p <- runif(2)
    n <- s[[2]]-s[[3]]
    if(p[[1]]<q.B+delta-n*alpha){
      s[[3]]<- s[[3]]+1
      if(p[[2]]<p.A+(n-1)*alpha) s[[2]] <- s[[2]]+1
    }else{
      if(p[[2]]<p.A+delta+n*alpha) s[[2]] <- s[[2]]+1
    }
    s[[1]] <- s[[1]]+1
    s
  }
  
  # 
  pk.ABAB <- function(){
    s <- c(0,0,0)  # 
    while (!pk.end(s)) {
      # A
      s <- pk.AtoB(s)
    }
    return(s[[2]]>s[[3]])
  }
  pk.ABBA <- function(){
    s <- c(0,0,0)  # 
    while (!pk.end(s)) {
      # A
      if(s[[1]]%%2==0) s <- pk.AtoB(s)
      else s <- pk.BtoA(s)
    }
    return(s[[2]]>s[[3]])
  }
  
  # 
  r1 <- vector("logical",n)
  r2 <- vector("logical",n)
  for (i in 1:n) {
    r1[[i]] <- pk.ABAB()
    r2[[i]] <- pk.ABBA()
  }
  
  return(list(m1=mean(r1),m2=mean(r2)))

}
